item.description: Title: IT Specialist Full Stack Operations and Development Company: CCA Software Pty Ltd (2008 - Present) Overview: I am an IT Specialist with over 13 years of experience at CCA Software Pty Ltd. Starting as a Tech and Customer Support Specialist for mainframe and third-party products, I advanced through the ranks to handle complex system and software management. My knowledge and skills, which are self-taught and developed through self-directed learning outside of work hours, demonstrate my commitment to personal and professional growth.
